bangaram ( english : gold ) is an indian telugu-language film which released on 3 may 2006 and was directed by tamil director dharani . this film has pawan kalyan in the lead role as the titular character and meera chopra , raja abel , reema sen , ashutosh rana , and mukesh rishi playing the supporting roles . this was a hit movie latter dubbed in hindi with the name ' &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; - the target '